310
00:21:28,500 --> 00:21:32,500
Mana cermin mata saya?

311
00:21:32,500 --> 00:21:34,250
Apa? Siapa peduli?

312
00:21:34,580 --> 00:21:37,160
Awak tak perlukan cermin mata lagi.

313
00:21:41,160 --> 00:21:43,250
Bagus, Zeke.

314
00:21:43,540 --> 00:21:46,000
Akhirnya awak belajar cara
baling bola dengan bagus.

315
00:21:55,330 --> 00:21:57,790
Awak nak jadi pemain besbol
bila awak dah besar nanti?

316
00:21:59,200 --> 00:22:00,540
Tidak...

317
00:22:01,080 --> 00:22:02,580
En. Ksaver...

